overview.en: ICOTH is a project jointly approved by the Ministry of Finance of the People's Republic of China, the Central Bank, the Ministry of Commerce, the Ministry of Economic Development, the National Investment Promotion Committee and the National Securities Commission. It is the first ICO integrated service platform in the world to receive a formalized legalization license.
overview.zh: 泰国东盟ICO研究院（ICOTH）是由泰国财政部、中央银行、商务部、经济发展部、全国促进投资委员会和国家证券委员会六部门联合审批通过的项目，是全球首个获得正式合法化牌照的ICO综合服务平台
